  Kau3 ui7 jip8 mng5, i ia7 toe3 Siu2-gi7 jip8-khi3. Siu2-gi7 kap lau7-bu2 chheng2-an au7 chhut-lai5 thiaN-nih, chiah khoaN3-tioh8 nng7 e5 chhiN-hun7 lang5-kheh, chiu7 mng7 lang5-kheh lin2 tui3 to2-ui7 lai5, chhiaN2 che7. Lang5-kheh in3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 tui3 Hui-lip8-pin lai5.¡¨ Peng5-si5 Siu2-gi7 bat thiaN a-kong kong2, koh bak8-chiu kim-kim ka7 i siong3, sim-te2 ia7 chin ki5-koai3 chit-e5 lang5-kheh e5 bin7-heng5, the2-thai3, siaN-im thai2 e7 kap i hiah sio-siang7. Tui3 an2-ni bo5 khoa3 koh kong2-oe7, kin2 jip8-khi3 ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2, ¡§Ma-mah goa7-bin7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5-kheh, ia7 hit-e5 lang5-kheh kong2 si7 tui3 Hui-lip8-pin lai5 e5 Hoa5-kiau5, i e5 bin7-heng5, the2-thai3, kong2-oe7 e5 siaN-im kap goa2 chin saN-seng5.¡¨ Ma-mah ka7 i kong2, ¡§Li2 ka7 i chheng2-mng7 i e5 toa7-mia5, i na7 kong2 si7 Tan5 Chheng-choaN5, li2 chiah chhiaN2 i lai5 kap a-bu2 chheng2-an.¡¨ Siu2-gi7 chhut-khi3 mng7 lang5-kheh e5 toa7-mia5, ko2-chin si7 Tan5 Chheng-choaN5. Siu2-gi7 chiu7 chhiaN2 i jip8-khi3 kong2, ¡§Sian-siN, khah sit-le2, goan2 ka-bo2 kong2 beh ka7 li2 chheng2-an.¡¨ Chheng-choaN5 chiu7 jip8-khi3. Chit8 e7 khoaN3 ko2-jian5 si7 Lan5-hiong. Lan5-hiong sui-jian5 si7 phoa3-piN7, ji5-chhiaN2 chin siong-tiong7, m7-ku2 tai7-ke ia7 si7 iau2 e7 jin7-tit. Tai7-ke tui3-khoaN3, bo5 oe7 hau2 chit8 khun3, jian5-au7 tui3 Siu2-gi7 kap Li7-na2 e5 an-ui3 chiah tai7-ke bo5 koh hau2. 
  Lan5-hiong chiah tui3 thau5 kau3 boe2 siong5-se3 kong2 chit8 pian3 hou7 Chheng-choaN5 thiaN. Chheng-choaN5 thiaN liau2 hui-siong5 e5 kian3-siau3, chu7-chek, ia7 chin kam2-kek, chap8-hun e5 tong5-cheng5, koh chin siong-sim. Chiah chai Lan5-hiong e5 kho2-chhu2, siu2-chiat, u7 chi3-khi3, ia7 Siu2-gi7 ko2-jian5 si7 i e5 hiat-thong2, kut-jiok8 e5 chhin, chin hoaN-hi2 i u7 chhin-siN e5 kiaN2. Koh chai si7 chin chiaN5-mih8 e5 kiaN2, sou2-i2 hui-siong5 hoaN-hi2, kam2-sia7 Lan5-hiong e5 cheng5. Jian5-au7 Chheng-choaN5 ia7 chhim-chhim jin7-choe7, soa3 kong2-khi2 i koe3-khi3 e5 cheng5-heng5, kam5 bak8-sai2 khan Lan5-hiong e5 chhiu2 kong2, ¡§Lan5, kiu5 li2 sia3-bian2 goa2.¡¨ Nng7 lang5 kong2 liau2-au7, tai7-ke koh hau2 chit8 khun3, chit pai2 lian5 Siu2-gi7 ia7 hau2. Li7-na2 khoaN3 tai7-ke hau2, i ia7 hau2. Hau2 liau2 tai7-ke chiah sio jin7. 
  Ui7-tioh8 koe3-thau5 e5 heng-hun3, Lan5-hiong hit mi5 koh chhut chin-che7 huih, keh-jit8 koh khah soe-jiok8, ia7 hoat koan5-jiat8. Tui3 an2-ni Chheng-choaN5 ti7 hia lai5 chiam5-sim chiau3-kou3 i. Siu2-gi7, Li7-na2 ia7 chin un-khun5 tau3 kou3 ma-mah. Na7-si7 i2-keng siuN ban7 lah. Keh-jit8 pai3 5 cha2-khi2 8 tiam2, Lan5-hiong ti7 tiong7-hu, kiaN2, cha-bou2-kiaN2 chiau3-kou3 e5 e7-bin7, peng5-an lai5 li7-khui se3-kan. Beh tng7-khui3 e5 si5 tui3 i e5 tiong7-hu Chheng-choaN5 kau-tai3 nng7 ku3 oe7. 
